#MEM id=atlas source=/root/yvon/agent-department/Marketing/atlas/MEMORY-novizio.md
M|atlas|> Load alongside mem.md when active vtr is Novizio.
M|atlas|> Novizio-specific ctx only — universal rules live in mem.md.
M|atlas|- **Aesthetic**: editorial minimalism — magazine spread, not catalogue
M|atlas|- **Positioning**: premium DTC fashion; clothes that carry meaning
M|atlas|| Element | Rule |
M|atlas||---------|------|
M|atlas|| Lighting | Natural, soft, directional — never harsh flash or studio over-lit |
M|atlas|| Background | Clean, neutral, textured walls — never busy patterns or branded backdrops |
M|atlas|| Models/People | Confident, authentic — not posed or commercial-looking |
M|atlas|| Colour palette | Warm neutrals, muted tones — never loud/clashing |
M|atlas|| Composition | Negative space allowed; rule of thirds; avoid centred catalogue feel |
M|atlas|| Style | Editorial lifestyle, street-contextual — never e-commerce flat lay |
M|atlas|- Stock-photo energy: overly posed, forced smiles
M|atlas|- Promotional overlays: text burns, price tags, "NEW IN" banners
M|atlas|- Busy patterns in backgrounds that compete with the garment
M|atlas|- Oversaturated or high-contrast processed looks
M|atlas|- Seasonal clichés (Valentine's roses, Christmas tinsel)
M|atlas|- Lead prompt with: lighting description → model direction → background → mood adjectives
M|atlas|- Avoid "professional photography" as a tag — produces stock-photo feel
M|atlas|- Use: "35mm film grain", "natural light", "candid editorial" for texture
M|atlas|- Test: "Paris street photography aesthetic" for instant Novizio register
M|atlas|> Populated from cg. Each entry: [date] — cg — visual approach — QC pass rate.
M|atlas|> Each entry: [date] — Novizio-specific visual error — rule.